on and Apogee Pacific, but never exchanged funds with either company. =E2=
=80=9CI smelled something I didn=E2=80=99t like.=E2=80=9D</p></blockquote><=
p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Or there is a Colombian model who =E2=80=9Csign=
ed a letter of intent in English, which stated, in part, that her nonprofit=
